Please proof read your website recipes. It is unfortunate that your website failed to mention the addition of broth to the recipe otherwise required for baking in a dish according to the Bon Appetit recipe (Nov. 2002). 3/4 to 1 and 1/2 cups of broth, according to the magazine. Also your web site prescribed baking uncovered; Bon Appetit called for baking covered. These changes made a difference: the result from your website printout was a far cry from your magazine published version.

